<note n="0567007" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0567007">（清）＋淨【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0567008" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0567008">答＋（耶）【元】【明】</note>
