<note n="0568003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0568003">卷第七首【三】【宮】，（摩訶般若波羅蜜）七字＝（小品般若波羅蜜經）八字【宋】【元】【宮】＊，〔摩訶般若波羅蜜〕－【明】＊</note>
<note n="0568004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0568004">向＝白【明】</note>
