<note n="0568008" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0568008">（有）＋人【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0568009" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0568009">伎＝技【元】，枝【明】</note>
<note n="0568010" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0568010">鍊＝練【三】【宮】＊</note>
