<note n="0569003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0569003">人＋（此人）【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0569004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0569004">〔如是〕－【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0569005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0569005">力＋（故）【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0569006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0569006">是以＝以是【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0569007" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0569007">〔及〕－【宋】【宮】</note>
